ead_reason":"strong gravitational lensing","topics":["Strong Gravitational Lensing"]},{"id":"2607.18440","canonical_id":"2607.18440","version_count":1,"previous_versions":[],"title":"Vz-GAL Dusty Star-Forming Galaxies: Revisiting the CO-H2 Conversion Factor Tension","authors":["Prachi Prajapati","Axel Weiss","Dominik Riechers","Tom J. L. C. Bakx","Leindert A. Boogaard","Diana Ismail","Pierre Cox","Andrew J. Baker","Roberto Neri","Matthew Lehnert","Chentao Yang","Emilio Romano-Diaz","Hiddo S. B. Algera","Stefano Berta","Edoardo Borsato","Kirsty M. Butler","Asantha Cooray","Bethany Jones","Amelie Saintonge","Paul van der Werf"],"categories":["astro-ph.GA"],"summary":"本研究利用21个高红移（z=1-4）尘埃星暴星系（DSFGs）的最大均匀样本，结合VLA的CO(1-0)观测和ALMA高分辨率1mm尘埃连续谱成像，重新审视了CO-to-H₂转换因子αCO的争论。通过尘埃SED建模和LVG框架推导分子气体质量，发现αCO的中值接近银河系值4.3（范围1.5-11.5），挑战了此前流行的αCO=0.8。研究表明，采用合理的气体尺度时，各向同性维里质量与气体质量一致，而\"混合\"模型会低估动力学质量。当前数据并不强制要求αCO=0.8，近银河系值在动力学上仍是可行的。","date":"2026-07-22","url":"https://arxiv.org/abs/2607.18440","score":95,"stars":5,"tier":"recommended","mandatory":false,"score_breakdown":[{"label":"high-z galaxy gas","points":20}],"must_read_reason":"","topics":["Multi-phase and Molecular Gas","Dust and ISM"]},{"id":"2607.14355","canonical_id":"2607.14355","version_count":1,"previous_versions":[],"title":"VENUS: an ultra-faint galaxy hosting the metal-poor type II supernova at $z=5.13$ Witnessing the initial metal enrichment with extremely frequent core-collapse supernovae?","authors":["Yoshihisa Asada","Seiji Fujimoto","Joseph F. V. Allingham","David A. Coulter","Conor Larison","Matthew R. Siebert","Gabriel Brammer","Dan Coe","Pratika Dayal","Qinyue Fei","Lukas J. Furtak","Vasily Kokorev","Keiichi Maeda","Richard Pan","Johan Richard","Fengwu Sun","Abdurro'uf","Jacqueline Antwi-Danso","Franz E. Bauer","Marusa Bradac","Larry D. Bradley","Volker Bromm","John Chisholm","Christopher J. Conselice","Christa DeCoursey","Anderas L. Faisst","Brenda Frye","Mauro Gonzalez-Otero","Yuichi Harikane","Tiger Y. Y. Hsia