lse,"score_breakdown":[],"must_read_reason":"","topics":["Dust and ISM"]},{"id":"2607.17144","canonical_id":"2607.17144","version_count":1,"previous_versions":[],"title":"Microlensing of Microlensing: Effects of Random Stars on the Double-Source-Plane Gravitational Lens","authors":["Nada Salama","Daniel J. Ballard","Huimin Qu","Geraint F. Lewis","Karl Glazebrook"],"categories":["astro-ph.CO"],"summary":"本文首次对双源平面引力透镜系统中的“复合微引力透镜效应”（微引力透镜的微引力透镜）进行了数值模拟，以J1721+8842系统为例，发现次级微透镜效应会产生更复杂的焦散结构，并影响各像的光变曲线。","date":"2026-07-21","url":"https://arxiv.org/abs/2607.17144","score":78,"stars":4,"tier":"recommended","mandatory":false,"score_breakdown":[{"label":"gravitational lens modelling","points":28}],"must_read_reason":"","topics":["Other Selected Research"]},{"id":"2607.19491","canonical_id":"2607.19491","version_count":1,"previous_versions":[],"title":"Rapid growth in a dual AGN during a gas-rich merger at z~4.5","authors":["Hyewon Suh","Roberto Decarli","Emanuele Paolo Farina","Julia Scharwächter","Mar Mezcua","Giorgio Lanzuisi","Federica Loiacono","Brian C. Lemaux","Sukyoung K. Yi","Stefano Marchesi","Marta Volonteri","Günther Hasinger","Francesca Civano","Anniek Gloudemans","Ena Choi","Yeonwoo Nam","Adi Foord","Silvia Onorato"],"categories":["astro-ph.GA"],"summary":"在红移z~4.5处发现了一对距离仅1.5 kpc的双活动星系核（LID-1166），这是首个超出局域宇宙的近距离双AGN系统，通过JWST和ALMA证实了两个正在活跃吸积的超大质量黑洞，揭示了早期宇宙中隐藏的并合驱动双AGN群体。","date":"2026-07-23","url":"https://arxiv.org/abs/2607.19491","score":73,"stars":4,"tier":"recommended","mandatory":false,"score_breakdown":[{"label":"high-z galaxy gas","points":20}],"must_read_reason":"","topics":["Multi-phase and Molecular Gas"]},{"id":"2607.19471","canonical_id":"2607.19471","version_count":1,"previous_versions":[],"title":"The first dusty galaxies across $6 \\lesssim z \\lesssim 14$: Blue monsters, red monsters, and the bimodality of dust content in early galaxies","authors":["Sergio Martínez-González","Casiana Muñoz-Tuñón","Santiago Jiménez"],"categories":["astro-ph.GA","